  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1 - \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf \u0baa\u0bc6\u0ba3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Support for protesters - inquiry into British woman",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is understood that investigations have been started from the point of view of whether she violated the visa regulations regarding a British woman who is said to have acted in support of the Khali face mask protest.",
        "It is understood that these investigations have been initiated in connection with a 'therapist' who is said to have been staying in Neer Colombo and Malabe areas since August 14, 2019 under a medical residency visa permit.",
        "It is reported that this woman named kayzfra5er has posted videos of the protest landscape through her Instagram page and home page, depicting sensitive issues of the security forces giving abuse to the protestors and inviting people from abroad to protest.",
        "At this stage, based on the advice given by the Ministry of Defense based on the reports of the intelligence department, the Department of Immigration and Emigration has paid attention to whether the woman in question has violated the visa procedures and whether to extend her resident visa after this."
      ],
